Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:34.77,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,493)\fad(1658,0)}赤紅之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城惠也沒預料到事情會變成這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來不能打醬油了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般來說 當城鎮這些居住點為襲擊目標的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該在盡量遠離城鎮的地方迎戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算擊退了敵人 但是導致城鎮受到了損害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對日後的生活也有影響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 由於不能用念話 請保持開啟隊伍頻道狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和五十鈴姐一起跟我們匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然敵人的等級不是很高 但是數量龐大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 只能去面對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠2小姐沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位姐姐可比我們厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能鬆手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑟拉拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是很意外的冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼一說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧德賽騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們要去和飛龍戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以城裡的人們也很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也趕緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ms.五十鈴 Ms.五十鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥已經開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ms.五十鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:04:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我倫迪浩斯·寇德在 盡可放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薩菲爾小鎮 Ms.五十鈴 Ms.實莉和Ms.瑟拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定都會被我熱情的光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都這種時候了就別瞎鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ms.五十鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哇哇 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雲雀之靴的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我現在的等級 雖然還不能在天上飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可以無視地形 大幅提高移動速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說跑得更快嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是天才啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別得寸進尺了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡 朝這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬彌 冬彌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來這裡 來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武士的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,束縛吼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(640,670)}AnchorhHowl
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了 瞬一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也算我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰 連協 什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂拉仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事啊 他們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裡 帶我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 已經回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經是第三回了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這羨慕你那破裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底怎麼回事 都在幹些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是復活裝置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大神殿一樣 再生場所的指向標
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計是誰的發明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠2姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臉色不太好啊 冬彌少年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好趣！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不好的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 一點都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是按照這個世界的法則產生的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這樣看來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們這是很積極的在提供「共感子」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種死的頻率使採集率變得很高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對「採集者」的幫助是很大的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不做點什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看來他們就是這樣希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們渴望死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像麻醉劑一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了那一瞬的走馬燈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是隆達格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周圍沒有異樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法軌道也很順暢
