Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從隆達格卿那裡的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 薄野那敗犬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是冒險者就當貴族對待嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從偵查的夢魘侍從來的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧德賽騎士團和鳥怪進入了交戰狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派出侍從 半數以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狀態都安定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從20號機開始同步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經驗值模擬器開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊伍頻道打開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:08:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召喚投影了大地人意識的夢魘侍從
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個得到的經驗值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會屬於召喚其出來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算侍從死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對他本人沒有任何影響
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是相當於給了大地人暫時的不死之軀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑聲真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別打斷話題啊臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1002,710)}好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說要用這傢伙來提升等級嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那效率真是高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你們冒險者所說的能量值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 10分鐘後開始使用EXP瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那很危險 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翠葉大人 一彥閣下要求中止投藥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他的偽善者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊是冒險者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊是大地人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會死的人懂個屁的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命凋零就是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到根本我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們究竟為什麼要構建這種低效率的社會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗影侍從
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從哪出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快保護我們的神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其實要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可知世界比不可知世界狹小的多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以理解的領域猶如針尖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不明白的事本身其實沒什麼不可思議的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬彌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小冬彌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡有沒有逃掉的大地人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旋風斬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實莉你不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠2小姐到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從哪裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個問題已經是第二回了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然出現…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算打倒了也沒有落魄的光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ms.五十鈴沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有喘不過氣啊
